2Trump%20Was%20Concerned%20About%20Wife's%20Reaction%2C%20Says%20Ex%20Aide%20At%20Hush%20Money%20Trial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20former%20close%20advisor%20to%20Donald%20Trump%20testified%20in%20court%20Friday%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bcrisis%26quot%3B%20that%20engulfed%20his%202016%20presidential%20campaign%20after%20a%20tape%20emerged%20of%20him%20bragging%20about%20groping%20women.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHope%20Hicks%20was%20the%20first%20ex-member%20of%20Trump's%20inner%20circle%20to%20take%20the%20stand%20in%20his%20historic%20criminal%20trial%20--%20in%20which%20he%20stands%20charged%20of%20falsifying%20business%20records%20to%20cover%20up%20hush%20money%20payments%20to%20a%20porn%20star%20to%20avoid%20another%20scandal%20before%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(I)%20was%20a%20little%20stunned%2C%26quot%3B%20Hicks%20said%20of%20the%20now%20infamous%20Access%20Hollywood%20tape%20in%20which%20Trump%20was%20heard%20boasting%20about%20grabbing%20women's%20genitalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20consensus%20among%20us%20all%20that%20the%20tape%20was%20damaging%2C%20this%20was%20a%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHicks%20was%20subpoenaed%20to%20appear%20by%20the%20prosecution%2C%20which%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20panic%20engendered%20by%20the%20tape%20triggered%20a%20Trump%20campaign%20effort%20to%20silence%20adult%20film%20star%20Stormy%20Daniels%20over%20her%20claim%20of%20a%20sexual%20encounter%20with%20the%20married%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20trial%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Trump%20is%20accused%20of%20reimbursing%20his%20then-lawyer%2C%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20for%20a%20%24130%2C000%20payment%20to%20Daniels%20just%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%202016%20election%20against%20Hillary%20Clinton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20and%20its%20revelations%20have%20gripped%20the%20legal%20and%20political%20establishment%20as%20Trump%20seeks%20to%20re-take%20the%20White%20House%20from%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20at%20November%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHicks%20admitted%20being%20nervous%20when%20she%20started%20to%20testify%2C%20and%20later%20burst%20into%20tears%20under%20cross-examination%20from%20Trump's%20often%20forceful%20attorney%20Emil%20Bove%2C%20prompting%20the%20judge%20to%20order%20a%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHicks%20was%20a%20key%20player%20in%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20Trump's%20successful%202016%20presidential%20campaign%20when%20hush%20money%20payments%20to%20Daniels%20were%20allegedly%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20reported%20to%20Mr%20Trump%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20campaign%2C%20Hicks%20told%20the%20court%2C%20describing%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20involved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EUltimate%20insider%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHicks%2C%20then%20aged%2026%2C%20joined%20Trump's%20longshot%20campaign%20in%202015%2C%20handpicked%20from%20a%20job%20at%20his%20daughter%20Ivanka's%20clothing%20business%2C%20becoming%20one%20of%20his%20most%20trusted%20lieutenants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20cut%20the%20former%20model%20out%20after%20her%20criticism%20emerged%20of%20his%20conduct%20when%20Trump%20supporters%20stormed%20the%20US%20Capitol%20on%20January%206%2C%202021%20to%20try%20to%20overturn%20his%20election%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20reportedly%20still%20has%20cordial%20relations%20with%20the%20Trump%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHicks%20also%20told%20the%20jury%20Friday%20of%20Trump's%20response%20to%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20story%20claiming%20he%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20a%20former%20Playboy%20model%2C%20Karen%20McDougal%2C%20whom%20he%20then%20allegedly%20paid%20off%20--%20a%20case%20echoing%20the%20alleged%20affair%20with%20Daniels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20concerned%20about%20how%20it%20would%20be%20viewed%20by%20his%20wife%26quot%3B%20Melania%2C%20Hicks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20declined%20to%20answer%20reporters'%20questions%20about%20Hicks%20during%20a%20break%20in%20p