%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A61%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68950907%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68950907.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68950907.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Mumbai%20Indians%20ki%20kahani%20khatam'%3A%20What%20went%20wrong%20for%20Hardik%20%26amp%3B%20Co%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714785074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109829739%2Cimgsize-86858.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fmumbai-indians-ki-kahani-khatam-what-went-wrong-for-five-time-ipl-champions%2Farticleshow%2F109829722.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Indians%20are%20virtually%20eliminated%20from%20contention%20for%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs.%20This%20season%20has%20been%20one%20of%20their%20most%20challenging%20in%20IPL%20history.%20Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20his%20team%20suffered%20their%20eighth%20loss%20in%2011%20matches%2C%20succumbing%20to%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20by%2024%20runs%20at%20their%20home%20turf%2C%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%2C%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Researchers%20Reconstruct%20Face%20Of%2075%2C000-Year-Old%20Neanderthal%20Woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20team%20of%20archaeologists%20in%20the%20UK%20unveiled%20the%20reconstructed%20face%20of%20a%2075%2C000-year-old%20Neanderthal%20woman%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EGiving%20an%20insight%20into%20how%20the%20woman%20would%20have%20looked%20when%20she%20was%20alive%2C%20the%20face%20was%20reconstructed%20using%20a%20smashed%20skull%20found%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20AFP%2C%20the%20woman%20has%20been%20named%20Shanidar%20Z%2C%20after%20the%20cave%20in%20Iraq's%20Kurdistan%20where%20the%20skull%20was%20discovered.%20This%20discovery%20also%20led%20to%20the%20investigation%20of%20over%2040%20Neanderthal%20women%2C%20who%20were%20laid%20to%20rest%20in%20a%20sleeping%20position%20beneath%20a%20huge%20vertical%20stone%20marker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68922877%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20face%20was%20assembled%20out%20of%20the%20shattered%20remains%20of%20the%20skull.%20The%20report%20claimed%20the%20bones%20were%20extremely%20soft%20like%20%26quot%3Ba%20well-dunked%20biscuit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBefore%20assembling%2C%20the%20researchers%20first%20had%20to%20strengthen%20the%20fragments.%20After%20this%2C%20the%20expert%20paleoartists%20created%20the%203D%20model%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20last%20Neanderthals%20mysteriously%20died%20around%2040%2C000%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20is%20just%20a%20few%20thousand%20years%20after%20humans%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20AFP%20report%20stated%20that%20Shanidar%20Z's%20skull%20was%20flattened%20to%20a%20thickness%20of%20two%20centimetres%20(0.7%20inches)%2C%20possibly%20by%20a%20rock%20fall%2C%20which%20may%20have%20happened%20soon%20after%20she%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20still%20considered%20the%20best%20preserved%20Neanderthal%20find%20of%20this%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20news%20agency%2C%20University%20of%20Cambridge's%20Professor%20Graeme%20Barker%2C%20who%20led%20the%20excavations%2C%20said%20the%20team%20had%20%26quot%3Bnever%20expected%20to%20get%20more%20Neanderthals%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20lower%20part%20of%20Shanidar%20Z's%20skeleton%20was%20excavated%20in%201960%E2%80%94during%20ground-breaking%20excavations%20by%20American%20archaeologist%20Ralph%20Solecki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20same%20excavation%2C%20Ralph%20Slecki%20found%20the%20remains%20of%20at%20least%2010%20Neanderthals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Ralph's%20discovery%20of%20a%20cluster%20of%20bodies%2C%20wherein%20one%20was%20surrounded%20by%20a%20bunch%20of%20ancient%20pollen%2C%20made%20him%20argue%20that%20this%20was%20evidence%20of%20funerary%20rituals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETalking%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bflower%20burial%26quot%3B%20theory%2C%20Professor%20Graeme%20Barker%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20try%20and%20date%20these%20burials...%20to%20use%20the%20site%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20big%20debate%20about%20why%20the%20Neanderthals%20died%20out%2C%20and%20then%20we%20started%20finding%20these%20bits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShanidar%20Z%20is%20the%20fifth%20body%20to%20be%20identified%20in%20the%20cluster%20buried%20over%20at%20least%20several%20hundred%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20experts%20believe%20the%20stone%20was%20used%20as%20an%20identifier%20to%20allow%20the%20roaming%20Neanderthals%20to%20return%20to%20the%20same%20spot%20to%20bury%20their%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Cambridge%20palaeo-anthropologist%2C%20Emma%20Pomeroy%2C%20who%20uncovered%20Shanidar%20Z%2C%20stated%20that%20finding%20the%20skull%20and%20upper%20body%20had%20been%20both%20%26quot%3Bexciting%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bterrifying%26quot%3B.%20Ms%20Pomeroy%20added%20that%20the%20task%20had%20been%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20stakes%203D%20jigsaw%20puzzle%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714784700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fd2v3sqjc_neanderthal_625x300_04_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-researchers-reconstruct-the-face-of-75-000-year-old-neanderthal-woman-5580844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20team%20of%20archaeologists%20in%20the%20UK%20unveiled%20the%20reconstructed%20face%20of%20a%2075%2C000-year-old%20Neanderthal%20woman%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-researchers-reconstruct-the-face-of-75-000-year-old-neanderthal-woman-5580844%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-researchers-reconstruct-the-face-of-75-000-year-old-neanderthal-woman-5580844%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-researchers-reconstruct-the-face-of-75-000-year-old-neanderthal-woman-5580844%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Janhvi%20woos%20fans%20with%20her%20sporty%20avatar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714784635000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109829617%2Cimgsize-113318.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjanhvi-kapoor-scorches-up-social-media-with-her-sporty-mr-and-mrs-mahi-avatar-at-cricket-match-pics%2Farticleshow%2F109829588.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109829588.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJanhvi%20Kapoor%20showcased%20her%20sporty%20side%20as%20she%20lent%20her%20support%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%20as%20they%20clashed%20with%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20at%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20Friday%20evening.%20Rocking%20her%20team%20colours%2C%20Kapoor%20captivated%20attention%20in%20a%20cro