ired%20for%20protesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20are%20protesting%20Israel's%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20it%20launched%20after%20a%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Oct.%207%20that%20Israel%20says%20killed%201%2C200%20people.%20Israel%20has%20killed%20over%2034%2C000%20people%20in%20retaliation%2C%20according%20to%20Gaza%20health%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHO%20ARE%20THE%20PROTESTERS%20SUPPORTING%20PALESTINIANS%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPro-Palestinian%20protests%20have%20drawn%20students%2C%20faculty%20and%20outside%20activists%2C%20including%20of%20Jewish%20and%20Muslim%20faiths.%20The%20groups%20organizing%20the%20protests%20include%20Students%20for%20Justice%20in%20Palestine%20and%20Jewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20encampments%20have%20hosted%20a%20diverse%20array%20of%20teach-ins%2C%20interfaith%20prayers%20and%20musical%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganizers%20have%20disavowed%20violence%20against%20pro-Israel%20counter-protesters%2C%20although%20some%20Jewish%20students%20have%20said%20they%20feel%20unsafe%20on%20campus%20and%20unnerved%20by%20chants%20they%20call%20antisemitic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20city%20leaders%20and%20university%20administrators%20have%20said%20activists%20from%20outside%20campus%20have%20co-opted%20or%20orchestrated%20protests.%20The%20University%20of%20Texas%2C%20Austin%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20said%20of%20the%2079%20people%20arrested%20on%20its%20campus%20on%20April%2029%2C%2045%20had%20no%20affiliation%20with%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHO%20ARE%20THE%20COUNTER%20PROTESTERS%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECampus%20counter%20protests%20have%20been%20led%20by%20Israeli%20American%20and%20Zionist%20groups%20as%20well%20as%20fellow%20students%20and%20Jewish-American%20community%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20people%20attended%20a%20counter%20rally%20at%20UCLA%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20organized%20by%20the%20Israel%20advocacy%20group%20the%20Israeli%20American%20Council.%20A%20Jewish%20student%20activist%20at%20UCLA%20posted%20video%20of%20himself%20being%20barred%20from%20an%20area%20of%20campus%20by%20pro-Palestinian%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20scuffle%20broke%20out%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%20on%20May%201%20between%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Zionist%20group%20Students%20Supporting%20Israel%20and%20a%20pro-Palestinian%20protester.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Arizona%20State%20University%20student%20counter%20protesters%20helped%20police%20dismantle%20a%20protest%20encampment%20on%20April%2027.%20Hundreds%20of%20students%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Mississippi%2C%20some%20waving%20U.S.%20flags%20and%20banners%20supporting%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20chanted%20against%20pro-Palestinian%20protesters%20on%20May%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20HAS%20BEEN%20THE%20RESPONSE%20FROM%20AUTHORITIES%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20school%20administrators%20have%20called%20in%20local%20law%20enforcement%20to%20arrest%20protesters%20and%20clear%20camps%20and%20sit%20ins.%20Others%20have%20let%20camps%20operate%20or%20reached%20deals%20to%20end%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColumbia%20sent%20in%20police%20on%20April%2018%2C%20a%20day%20after%20students%20set%20up%20a%20camp%20on%20the%20Manhattan%20campus.%20On%20April%2030%20police%20again%20raided%20the%20camp%20and%20a%20building%20occupied%20by%20students%2C%20making%20hundreds%20of%20arrests.%20President%20Minouche%20Shafik%20said%20the%20camp%20was%20an%20unauthorized%20protests%20that%20had%20made%20the%20campus%20%26quot%3Bintolerable%26quot%3B%20for%20many%20Jewish%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%20has%20allowed%20a%20pro-Palestinian%20camp%20so%20long%20as%20it%20does%20not%20disrupt%20campus%20operations%20and%20there%20is%20no%20threat%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorthwestern%20University%2C%20Brown%20University%20and%20Rutgers%20University%20are%20among%20colleges%20that%20have%20reached%20deals%20to%20disband%20camps.%20Brown%20will%20hold%20a%20vote%20on%20possible%20divestment%20from%20firms%20connected%20with%20Israel.%20Rutgers%20agreed%20to%20set%20up%20an%20Arab%20cultural%20center%20and%20look%20into%20creation%20of%20a%20Middle%20East%20studies%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20HAS%20BEEN%20THE%20IMPACT%20ON%20REGULAR%20CAMPUS%20LIFE%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EColumbia%20has%20at%20times%20had%20to%20switch%20to%20all-virtual%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%20called%20off%20its%20main-stage%20graduation%20ceremony%20after%20canceling%20the%20valedictorian%20speech%20by%20a%20Muslim%20student%20and%20dozens%20of%20arrests%20after%20police%20cleared%20a%20pro-Palestinian%20encampment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20State%20Polytechnic%20University%2C%20Humboldt%2C%20canceled%20in-person%20classes%20after%20students%20barricaded%20themselves%20in%20an%20administrative%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Michigan%20said%20it%20would%20allow%20free%20expression%20and%20peaceful%20protest%20at%20its%20early%20May%20graduation%20ceremonies%20but%20would%20stop%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%20disruption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHOW%20ARE%20POLITICAL%20LEADERS%20RESPONDING%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20has%20been%20criticized%20by%20the%20protesters%20for%20supplying%20funding%20and%20weapons%20to%20Israel%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Americans%20had%20the%20right%20to%20demonstrate%20but%20not%20to%20unleash%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20the%20Republican%20candidate%20for%20the%202024%20election%2C%20called%20the%20campus%20protests%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20hate%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20April%2030%20police%20raid%20on%20Columbia%20%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20be