eir%20own%20counter-drone%20capabilities%2C%20even%20when%20deploying%20to%20high-pressure%20regions%20such%20as%20the%20Pacific%2C%20where%20tensions%20with%20China%20are%20running%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnmanned%20aircraft%20systems%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20wicked%20problem%20that%20everyone's%20working%20hard%20to%20come%20to%20grips%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Col.%20Brendan%20Sullivan%2C%20then-commanding%20officer%20of%20Marine%20Rotational%20Force-Darwin%2C%20or%20MRF-D%2C%20told%20reporters%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20huge%20focus%20of%20effort%20within%20the%201st%20Marine%20Division%20and%20a%20specific%20emphasis%20going%20for%20the%20division%20commander.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20US%20marine%20in%20uniform%20points%20a%20rifle%20at%20aerial%20targets%20during%20exercise%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663537800dfb1341e9028ada%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Marines%20observed%20targets%20during%20a%20counter-unmanned%20aircraft%20system%20(UAS)%20range%20on%20Marine%20Corps%20Base%20Camp%20Lejeune%20in%20North%20Carolina.%3Cp%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%20photo%20by%20Lance%20Cpl.%20Anakin%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20units%2C%20such%20as%20the%2024th%20Marine%20Expeditionary%20Unit%2C%20have%20had%20their%20hands%20on%20counter-drone%20systems%20such%20as%20the%20Light%20Marine%20Air%20Defense%20Integrated%20System%2C%20or%20L-MADIS%2C%20the%20little%20brother%20to%20the%20system%20with%20a%20similar%20name%2C%20since%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Some%20MEUs%20have%20used%20it%20for%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20that%20drones%20present%20to%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20was%20a%20concern%20at%20last%20year's%20Modern%20Day%20Marine%20expo%2C%20with%20then-commandant%20Gen.%20David%20Berger%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthe%20defense%20against%20drones%20and%20swarming%20drones%20...%20