20news%20machine%20on%20Grok.%3Cp%3ERingo%20H.W.%20Chiu%2FAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20wants%20to%20combine%20Twitter%20and%20Grok%2C%20his%20AI%20engine%2C%20and%20create%20a%20news%20machine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Grok%20won't%20look%20for%20%26quot%3Bnews%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20it%20will%20look%20for%20%26quot%3Bthings%20people%20are%20saying%20on%20Twitter%20about%20news.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20several%20problems%20with%20this%20approach!%20But%20it%20may%20be%20the%20future%2C%20regardless.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20do%20you%20think%20of%20when%20you%20think%20of%20%26quot%3Bnews%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20both%20old%20and%20in%20the%20news%20business.%20So%20when%20I%20think%20of%20%26quot%3Bnews%2C%26quot%3B%20it's%20usually%20like%20%3Cem%3Esomething%20that%20comes%20from%20an%20organization%20that%20specializes%20in%20distributing%20and%20sometimes%20sourcing%2Fverifying%20facts%20about%20current%20events%3C%2Fem%3E.%20You%20know%3A%20like%20a%20newspaper%20or%20a%20website%20or%20TV%20show%2Fnetwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20thinks%20news%20is%20something%20different%3A%20It's%20%3Cem%3Ewhat%20people%20talk%20about%20on%20the%20service%20formerly%20known%20as%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdid-elon-musk-buy-twitter-acquisition-details%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETwitter%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20the%20vision%20he's%20using%20to%20build%20a%20news%20service%20at%20X%2C%20the%20company%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-grok-elon-musk-ai-chatbot-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20homegrown%20AI%20chatbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bigtechnology.com%2Fp%2Felon-musks-plan-for-ai-news%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk's%20idea%2C%20he%20tells%20journalist%20Alex%20Kantrowitz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20that%20the%20best%20way%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20news%20isn't%20by%20reading%2Flistening%20to%20the%20news%2C%20but%20by%20listening%20to%20what%20people%20%3Cem%3Esay%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EConversation%20on%20X%20will%20make%20up%20the%20core%20of%20Grok's%20summaries%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20really%20almost%20all%20of%20it.%20Musk%20said%20Grok%20will%20not%20look%20directly%20at%20article%20text%2C%20and%20will%20instead%20rely%20solely%20on%20social%20posts.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20summarizing%20what%20people%20say%20on%20X%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20just%20to%20make%20it%20clear%2C%20a%20Musk%20employee%20confirms%20to%20Kantrowitz%20that%20these%20are%20indeed%20his%20marching%20orders%3A%20%26quot%3BIgor%20Babuschkin%2C%20a%20technical%20staff%20member%20working%20at%20Musk's%20xAI%2C%20said%20his%20team%20is%20focused%20on%20'making%20Grok%20understand%20the%20news%20purely%20from%20what%20is%20posted%20on%20X.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELook.%20I%20know%20that%20%26quot%3Bunderstanding%20the%20news%20purely%20from%20what%20is%20posted%20on%20the%20company%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20going%20to%20give%20a%20lot%20of%20us%20comfort.%20Definitely%20not%20in%20the%20Elon%20Musk%20era%20of%20the%20company%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20kinda%20like%20it%3F%20In%20theory%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20be%20clear%3A%20Understanding%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20world%20based%20%3Cem%3Esolely%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20what%20people%20say%20on%20X%2C%20or%20any%20other%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20is%20Not%20A%20Good%20Idea.%20But%20consuming%20commentary%20about%20what%20people%20say%20about%20what's%20happening%20in%20the%20world%20isn't%20a%20terrible%20idea.%20Maybe%20even%20a%20good%20one%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20more%20practically%3A%20That%20kind%20of%20commentary%20consumption%20actually%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20way%20many%20people%20learn%20about%20what's%20happening%20in%20the%20world.%20Even%20if%20you're%20a%20Serious%20News%20Consumer%20(thank%20you!)%2C%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20information%20you're%20getting%20likely%20%3Cem%3Eisn't%3C%2Fem%3E%20directly%20from%20a%20primary%20news%20source%2C%20but%20from%20someone%20who%20has%20aggregated%20or%20at%20least%20repeated%20what%20a%20primary%20news%20source%20says.%20It's%20basic%20economics%3A%20It's%20very%20expensive%20to%20go%20find%20news%20for%20yourself%2C%20and%20very%20cheap%20to%20talk%20about%20things%20that%20are%20in%20the%20news%2C%20or%20to%20package%20and%20present%20news%20other%20people%20have%20procured.%20That's%20why%20even%20large%2C%20well-funded%20news%20outfits%20%E2%80%94%20take%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20CNN%20%E2%80%94%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20time%20discussing%20and%20debating%20things%20we've%20already%20heard%20about%2C%20instead%20of%20presenting%20you%20with%20new%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20use%20cases%20where%20generative%20AI%20doesn't%20do%20a%20great%20job%2C%20it%20does%20seem%20quite%20useful%20at%20summarizing%20existing%20information%2C%20particularly%20when%20it's%20already%20been%20typed%20up.%20So%20why%20not%20summarize%20commentary%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20to-be-sures%3A%20Yes%2C%20you'd%20be%20foolish%20to%20rely%20on%20an%20Elon%20Musk-run%20AI%20machine%20for%20factual%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EGrok%2C%20no...%20%3Ca