k's%20solution%2C%20as%20Kantrowitz%20points%20out%3A%20Right%20now%2C%20Musk%20is%20barely%20even%20trying%20to%20tell%20you%20about%20the%20original%20source%20of%20the%20information%20he's%20summarizing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20Grok%20to%20%26quot%3Btell%20me%20about%20Elon%20Musk's%20plan%20to%20summarize%20news%20using%20grok%26quot%3B%20it%20provided%20me%20a%20very%20cogent%20summary%20of%20Kantrowitz's%20piece.%20But%20to%20find%20the%20source%20of%20that%20summary%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20scroll%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20entry%2C%20then%20all%20the%20way%20to%20right%2C%20past%20other%20people's%20tweets%20with%20zero%20information%20about%20Musk's%20plans%2C%20to%20find%20Kantrowitz's%20tweet%20linking%20to%20his%20original%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20lousy%20way%20to%20give%20people%20access%20to%20more%20information.%20It's%20also%20lousy%20for%20publishers%20who%20are%20still%20spending%20effort%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Kantrowitz%20%E2%80%94%20to%20find%20new%20information.%20It%20means%20Musk%20gets%20the%20benefit%20of%20their%20work%20and%20they%20get%20next%20to%20nothing%20%E2%80%94%20barely%20even%20a%20link%20%E2%80%94%20in%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlas%2C%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20way%20we're%20headed%20with%20AI%20in%20general%3A%20Despite%20efforts%20to%20negotiate%20or%20sue%20Big%20AI%2C%20most%20publishers%20are%20headed%20to%20a%20world%20where%20Big%20AI%20engines%20provide%20increasingly%20complete%20answers%20to%20queries%20and%20give%20users%20little%20incentive%20to%20head%20to%20original%20sources%20to%20learn%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20certainly%20be%20nice%20if%20Grok%20gave%20Kantrowitz%20more%20prominent%20billing%20when%20it%20provides%20an%20answer%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it%20may%20or%20may%20not%20get%20around%20to%20doing%20that%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Frecode%2F2022%2F12%2F16%2F23512993%2Fdoxxing-elon-musk-twitter-journalist-ban%3Futm_campaign%3Dvox%26utm_con