ned%20this%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20massive%20story%20and%20make%20the%20news%20cycle%20for%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%2C%26quot%3B%20Hicks%20said%20on%20the%20witness%20stand%20earlier%20Friday%2C%20explaining%20her%20reaction%20to%20learning%20about%20the%20tape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20testimony%2C%20Hicks%20hurt%20Trump%20by%20showing%20how%20deeply%20he%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20campaign%20%E2%80%94%20worried%20about%20infidelity%20stories%20going%20public%20in%20the%20weeks%20before%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20became%20emotional%20as%20prosecutors%20wrapped%20up%20their%20direct%20examination%20of%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20final%20answer%20helped%20bolster%20the%20district%20attorney's%20case.%20She%20said%20Trump%20was%20happy%20that%20news%20of%20the%20hush-money%20arrangement%20with%20Daniels%20had%20become%20public%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20was%20Mr.%20Trump's%20feeling%20that%20it%20was%20better%20to%20be%20dealing%20with%20it%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Brather%20than%20just%20before%20the%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20took%20the%20witness%20stand%20again%20after%20about%20a%20five-minute%20break%2C%20looking%20flushed%20but%20calmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20the%20hallway%20after%20the%20court%20day%2C%20Trump%20declined%20to%20answer%20Business%20Insider's%20question%20about%20his%20reaction%20to%20Hicks's%20testimony%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20bound%20by%20the%20gag%20order%20that%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan%20imposed%2C%20preventing%20him%20from%20talking%20about%20witnesses.%20He%20pivoted%20to%20attacking%20the%20Manhattan%20district%20attorney's%20office%2C%20which%20he%20said%20has%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20ruined%20and%20destroyed%26quot%3B%20the%20lives%20of%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20great%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20destroyed%20people's%20lives.%20They've%20gone%20out%2C%20hired%20lawyers%2C%20they've%20been%20with%20lawyers%20for%20years.%20They%20suck%20dry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20a%20shame.%20It's%20a%20shame%20what%20they've%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHicks%20described%20the%20Trump%20campaign's%20frenzied%20reactions%20to%20the%20'Access%20Hollywood'%20tape%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20was%20one%20of%20Trump's%20most%20trusted%20advisors%20in%20his%202016%20climb%20to%20the%20presidency.%20Federal%20prosecutors%20have%20previously%20said%20in%20court%20papers%20from%20the%202019%20prosecution%20of%20Michael%20Cohen%20that%20she%20could%20directly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhope-hicks-kellyanne-conway-could-directly-link-trump-hush-money-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etie%20Trump%20to%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bcatch-and-kill%26quot%3B%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20formally%20joined%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20in%20October%202014%20after%20working%20with%20the%20company%20with%20the%20public%20relations%20firm%20Hiltzik%20Strategies.%20As%20Trump%20began%20running%20for%20president%2C%20in%202015%2C%20she%20switched%20to%20a%20campaign%20role%20and%20traveled%20with%20him%20across%20the%20country%2C%20she%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%2C%202016%20%E2%80%94%20less%20than%20a%20month%20before%20the%20election%20%E2%80%94%20Hicks%20received%20an%20email%20from%20Washington%20Post%20reporter%20David%20Fareholdt%2C%20informing%20her%20he%20had%20obtained%20the%20video%2C%20sending%20a%20transcript%20of%20Trump's%20remarks%20about%20grabbing%20women%20%26quot%3Bby%20the%20pussy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20requesting%20a%20response%20from%20Trump.%20She%20forwarded%20it%20to%20other%20campaign%20leaders%3A%20Jason%20Miller%2C%20David%20Bossie%2C%20Kellyanne%20Conway%2C%20and%20Steve%20Bannon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeny%20deny%20deny%2C%26quot%3B%20Hicks%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%2C%20suggesting%20one%20possible%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20then%20went%20to%20the%2025th%20floor%20of%20Trump%20Tower%2C%20she%20testified%2C%20where%20she%20said%20Trump%20was%20preparing%20for%20a%20presidential%20debate%20with%20Miller%2C%20Conway%2C%20Bannon%2C%20Jared%20Kushner%2C%20and%20Chris%20Christie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20weren't%20sure%20how%20to%20respond%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20testified%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20trying%20to%20obtain%20the%20information%20and%20were%20processing%20the%20shock%20internally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20responded%20%26quot%3Bthat%20that%20didn't%20sound%20like%20something%20he%20would%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20Hicks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20stunned%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20time%20and%20struggled%20to%20get%20her%20bearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20definitely%20concerned%20this%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20massive%20story%20and%20make%20the%20news%20cycle%20for%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20at%20least%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20consensus%20amongst%20us%20all%20that%20the%20tape%20was%20damaging%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20while%2C%20Trump%20presented%20a%20more%20dismissive%20attitude%2C%20Hicks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20two%20guys%20talking%2C%20locker%20room%20talk.%20It%20was%20something%20that%20we%20shouldn't%20get%20too%20concerned%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Hicks%20said%2C%20relaying%20Trump's%20attitude.%20%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20want%20to%20offend%20anybody%20but%20he%20felt%20it%20was%20pretty%20standard%20for%20two%20guys%20talking%20about%20somebody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20said%20media%20coverage%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAccess%20Hollywood%26quot%3B%20tape%20was%20so%20all-consuming%20that%20no%20one%20had%20paid%20attention%20to%20the%20Category%204%20hurricane%20that%20was%20expected%20to%20hit%20the%20East%20Coast%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20dominated%20media%20coverage%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20the%2036%20hours%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20debate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThen%20came%20the%20Stormy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20campaign%20realized%20it%20had%20a%20potential%20problem%20with%20female%20voters%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20tape's%20release%2C%20Hicks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20suggested%20that%20dynamic%20colored%20the%20reaction%20to%20another%20inquiry%20from%20a%20journalist%20%E2%80%94%20Michael%20Rothfeld%20at%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20%E2%80%94%20on%20November%204%2C%20just%20four%20days%20before%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20email%20came%20when%20Trump's%20private%20jet%20had%20landed%20in%20Ohio%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bhanger%20rally%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20plane%20in%20the%20background.%20Rothfeld%20had%20asked%20about%20a%20secret%20%24150%2C000%20arrangement%20between%20American%20Media%20Inc.%2C%20the%20publisher%20of%20the%20National%20Enquirer%2C%20and%20Karen%20McDougal.%20In%20the%20agreement%2C%20AMI%20bought%20the%20exclusive%20rights%20to%20McDougal's%20story%20about%20an%20affair%20the%20former%20Playboy%20bunny%20said%20she%20had%20with%20Trump%20in%202006%2C%20when%20he%20was%20married%20to%20Melania%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20but%20never%20published%20any%20articles%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20had%20a%20phone%20call%20with%20Rothfeld%2C%20where%20he%20also%20mentioned%20Stormy%20Daniels%2C%20she%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20tried%20to%20control%20the%20story%2C%20reaching%20out%20to%20Jared%20Kushner%2C%20who%20she%20said%20was%20friendly%20with%20the%20Journal's%20owner%20Rupert%20Murdoch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20had%20a%20very%20good%20relationship%20with%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20if%20we%20could%20buy%20a%20little%20extra%20time%20to%20deal%20with%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKushner%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bwasn't%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20Rupert%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20also%20said%20she%20reached%20out%20to%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20knowing%20he%20had%20a%20relationship%20with%20American%20Media%20Inc.%20owner%20David%20Pecker.%20And%20she%20reached%20out%20to%20Pecker's%20office%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPecker%20%26quot%3Bexplained%20that%20Karen%20Macdougal%20was%20paid%20for%20magazine%20covers%20and%20fitness%20columns%20and%20it%20was%20all%20very%20legitimate%2C%26quot%3B%20Hicks%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20was%20what%20the%20contract%20was%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20relaying%20that%20to%20Trump%2C%20Hicks%20said%20that%20Trump%20wanted%20to%20speak%20to%20Pecker%20himself%20and%20%26quot%3Bhave%20an%20understanding%20of%20what%20was%20going%20on.%26quot%3B%20On%20another%20phone%20call%2C%20with%20Trump%2C%20Pecker%20assured%20him%20the%20payment%20to%20McDougal%20was%20for%20fitness%20columns%2C%20Hicks%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20then%20personally%20crafted%20a%20campaign%20statement%20denying%20the%20accusations%20from%20McDougal%2C%20and%20any%20knowledge%20of%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20published%20Journal%20article%20made%20mention%20of%20a%20possible%20affair%20and%20similar%20deal%20with%20Stormy%20Daniels%2C%20but%20focused%20on%20McDougal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Journal%20published%20another%20article%2C%20in%202018%2C%20focused%20on%20the%20%24130%2C000%20Daniels%2C%20Hicks%20was%20at%20that%20point%20the%20White%20House%20communications%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20her%20that%20Cohen%20had%20paid%20the%20%24130%2C000%20in%20hush-money%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20the%20kindness%20of%20his%20own%20heart%26quot%3B%20to%20protect%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHicks%20testified%20she%20found%20Trump's%20explanation%20hard%20to%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20say%20that%20would%20be%20out%20of%20character%20for%20Michael%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20to%20laughter%20in%20the%20court's%20overflow%20room.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20know%20Michael%20to%20be%20an%20especially%20charitable%20person.%20Or%20selfless%20person.%20He's%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20who%20seeks%20credit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-hush-money-trial-hope-hicks-witness-stand-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714763869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6635077dec0c69656900d1cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-hush-money-trial-hope-hicks-witness-stand-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hope%20Hicks%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20most%20trusted%20advisors%2C%20took%20the%20witness%20stand%20on%20Friday%20in%20his%20Manhattan%20criminal%20trial.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano%2CJacob%20Shamsian%2CNatalie%20Musumeci)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-hush-money-trial-hope-hicks-witness-stand-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suhana%20reveals%20she%20has%20broken%20up%2C%20Shweta%20reacts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714763430000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109825566%2Cimgsize-71340.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsuhana-khan-reveals-she-has-broken-up-in-a-new-video-check-out-shweta-bachchan-nandas-reaction%2Farticleshow%2F109825535.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109825535.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESuhana%20Khan%2C%20who%20recently%20m