whom%20she%20had%20defeated%20in%202019%2C%20would%20not%20be%20contesting%20against%20her%20but%20would%20fight%20from%20Raebareli%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20said%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20for%20her%20that%20%26quot%3Ban%20ordinary%20BJP%20worker%20had%20sent%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20packing%26quot%3B.%20Raebareli%20was%20the%20only%20seat%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20how%20she%20saw%20the%20developments%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Women%20And%20Child%20Development%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20Congress%20nomination%20and%20the%20entire%20Gandhi%20family%20backing%20out%20from%20a%20battle%20in%20Amethi%20is%20significant%20because%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20am%20concerned%2C%20it%20is%20the%20proclamation%20of%20defeat%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20from%20Amethi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20Gandhi%20family%20loyalist%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20Amethi%20for%2040%20years%2C%20getting%20the%20ticket%20instead%20and%20the%20Congress%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20giving%20a%20chance%20to%20a%20grassroots%20worker%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20said%20people%20who%20have%20seen%20enough%20politics%20would%20know%20when%20they%20are%20being%20%26quot%3Bhoodwinked%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20an%20iota%20of%20chance%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20winning%2C%20they%20would%20have%20fought%20the%20battle%20here%20in%20Amethi%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20she%20would%20have%20wanted%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20contest%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20said%20she%20had%20already%20created%20history%20in%202019%20when%20she%20defeated%20the%20sitting%20Congress%20president.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Mr%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20run%20away%20from%20Amethi.%20He%20had%20run%20away%20in%202019%20as%20well.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20last%20time%20he%20sought%20comfort%20in%20Wayanad%20and%20this%20time%20he%20chose%20not%20to%20contest%20at%20all.%20So%20it%20is%20the%20second%20time%20Mr%20Gandhi%20shied%20away%20from%20a%20battle%20in%20Amethi%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Have%20Done%20Much%20In%20Life'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20she%20would%20have%20like%20to%20challenge%20him%20in%20Amethi%20as%20well%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20give%20him%20too%20much%20importance.%20I%20am%20a%20self-made%20woman.%20I%20have%20had%20a%202.5-decade%20successful%20career%20in%20media.%20I%20have%20been%20an%20MP.%20I%20have%20been%20announced%20as%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20global%20leader%20in%202015%20itself...%20I%20have%20done%20much%20in%20life.%20I%20don't%20need%20a%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20chase%20to%20make%20my%20career%20or%20my%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20by%20the%20way%2C%20I%20have%20done%20it%20without%20having%20a%20politician%20who%20is%20a%20father%20to%20me%20and%20the%20'karta%20dharta'%20(prime%20mover)%20of%20an%20entire%20political%20organisation.%20So%20I%20have%20done%20it%20without%20comfort%20and%20at%20personal%20cost%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20has%20not%20only%20let%20down%20his%20whole%20political%20organisation%2C%20but%20also%20his%20family%20legacy.%20I%20think%20it%20speaks%20volumes%20that%20an%20ordinary%20worker%20of%20the%20BJP%20could%20defeat%20the%20Gandhi%20scion.%20And%2C%20today%2C%20an%20ordinary%20worker%20of%20the%20BJP%20had%20the%20entire%20family%20packed%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20the%20Raebareli%20battle%2C%20where%20Mr%20Gandhi%20is%20up%20against%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20who%20had%20lost%20the%20seat%20in%202019%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20if%20the%20Congress%20leader%20was%20confident%20of%20winning%20from%20there%2C%20he%20would%20not%20have%20been%20contesting%20from%20Wayanad%20-%20where%20he%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20-%20as%20well.%20She%20said%20if%20the%20Gandhis%20were%20confident%2C%20former%20Congress%20President%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20would%20not%20have%20given%20up%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Death%20Knell'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Robert%20Vadra%20saying%20he%20wanted%20to%20contest%20from%20Amethi%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20doesn't%20think%20her%20son-in-law%20is%20competent%20enough%20to%20be%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%20that's%20a%20decision%20for%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20to%20take.%20It's%20nothing%20for%20me%20to%20ponder%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsisting%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20do%20well%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20proclamation%20from%20Amethi%20itself%20is%20indicative%20that%20this%20is%20the%20last%20death%20knell%20in%20the%20political%20coffin%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party...%20The%2079th%20(seat%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh)%20was%20proclaimed%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%20itself%20that%20they%20are%20losing.%20The%2080th%20is%20Raebareli.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20will%20surely%20lose%20from%20there.%20Else%20he%20would%20have%20never%20fought%20from%20Wayanad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20another%20dig%20at%20her%20former%20opponent%2C%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20remember%20Mr%20Gandhi%20is%20not%20fighting%20this%20battle%20alone.%20He%20has%20taken%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20So%20what%20kind%20of%20a%20leader%20is%20this%2C%20who%20can't%20fight%20his%20own%20battles%20alone%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20Worthy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Irani%20claimed%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20has%20declared%20her%20victory%20in%20Amethi%20with%20its%20decision%20and%20when%20she%20was%20asked%20whether%20Mr%20Sharma%20is%20a%20worthy%20opponent%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWas%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20worthy%20in%202019%3F%20He%20was%20an%20absentee%20MP.%20I'm%20a%20two-term%20MP%20who%20has%20never%20been%20absent.%20as%20compared%20to%20Mr%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20My%20spend%20of%20MP%20local%20area%20development%20funds%20and%20my%20record%20in%20Parliament%20has%20been%20pretty%20decent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20compared%20to%20somebody%20who%20is%20self-made%20and%20has%20been%20a%20productive%20MP%2C%20do%20you%20think%20an%20absentee%20MP%20who%20depended%20on%20a%20family%20name%20to%20become%20a%20politician%20is%20a%20worthy%20opponent%20for%20a%20person%20like%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20an%20MP%20only%20for%20five%20years%20as%20compared%20to%2050%20years%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%20I'm%20grateful%20that%20people%20in%20these%20five%20years%20have%20decided%20that%20I%20make%20for%20a%20better%20public%20representative%20than%20the%20Gandhis%20who%20were%20here%20for%2050%20years%2C%20and%20especially%20Mr%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20here%20as%20an%20absentee%20MP%20for%2015%20years.%20The%20comparison%20was%20stark%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20withdrew%20from%20contesting%20from%20its%20so-called%20family%20bastion%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalled%20a%20giant%20slayer%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20said%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20%26quot%3Bhardly%20a%20giant%26quot%3B%20and%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20writing%20is%20on%20the%20wall.%20As%20far%20as%20Amethi%20goes%2C%20they%20have%20woken%20up%20and%20smelled%20the%20coffee.%20I'm%20sure%20they%20will%20be%20coming%20to%20many%20realities%20on%20the%20fourth%20of%20June.%20The%20citizen%20had%20fallen%20long%20ago.%20They%20have%20now%20woken%20up%20to%20that%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20was%20not%20transparent%20with%20the%20voters%20of%20Wayanad%20in%202019%20about%20fighting%20another%20seat%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20field%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20from%20Amethi%20indicates%20that%20the%20Congress%20knows%20that%20it%20is%20not%20well%20positioned%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Ordinary%20Worker'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20she%20thought%2080%20on%2080%20is%20achievable%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%20is%20a%20great%20indicator%20of%20what%20is%20available%20in%20terms%20of%20political%20realities%20vis%20a%20vis%20the%20Congress%20Party.%20It%20is%20the%20Congress%20Party%20that%20has%20concluded%20that%20if%20any%20member%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20fights%20Amethi%2C%20they%20will%20lose.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20conclusion%20by%20the%20BJP.%20That%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20felt%20it%20not%20it%20did%20not%20have%20even%20a%20fighting%20chance%20in%20Amethi%20speaks%20volumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20remember%20this%20they%20are%20the%20first%20family%20of%20Indian%20politics.%20And%20I'm%20just%20an%20ordinary%20BJP%20worker.%20That%20an%20ordinary%20BJP%20worker%20could%20send%20them%20packing%20away%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20what%20awaits%20them%20on%20the%20fourth%20of%20June%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714763040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5c8t441_smriti-irani-interview_625x300_04_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-give-him-too-much-importance-smriti-iranis-swipe-at-rahul-gandhi-5583399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dripping%20confidence%20after%20the%20Congress%20decided%20not%20to%20field%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20against%20her%20in%20Amethi%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20has%20said%20this%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20Congress%20conceding%20the%2079th%20out%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20to%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A