20inherent%20in%20every%20marriage.%20Petty%20quibbles%2C%20trifling%20differences%20are%20mundane%20matters%20and%20should%20not%20be%20exaggerated%20and%20blown%20out%20of%20proportion%20to%20destroy%20what%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20made%20in%20heaven%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20observation%20came%20in%20a%20judgment%20that%20set%20aside%20a%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20order%2C%20which%20dismissed%20a%20husband's%20plea%20seeking%20the%20quashing%20of%20a%20criminal%20case%20lodged%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20many%20times%2C%20the%20parents%20and%20close%20relatives%20of%20a%20married%20woman%20make%20a%20mountain%20out%20of%20a%20molehill%20and%20instead%20of%20salvaging%20the%20situation%20and%20saving%20the%20marriage%2C%20their%20action%20brings%20about%20complete%20destruction%20of%20the%20marital%20bonds%20on%20trivial%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20said%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20comes%20to%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20woman%2C%20her%20parents%20and%20relatives%20is%20the%20police%2C%20as%20if%20that%20is%20the%20panacea%20of%20all%20evil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20sooner%20the%20matter%20reaches%20the%20police%2C%20even%20if%20there%20are%20fair%20chances%20of%20reconciliation%20between%20the%20spouses%2C%20they%20would%20get%20destroyed%2C%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20must%20appreciate%20that%20all%20quarrels%20must%20be%20weighed%20from%20that%20point%20of%20view%20in%20determining%20what%20constitutes%20cruelty%20in%20each%20particular%20case%2C%20always%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20physical%20and%20mental%20conditions%20of%20the%20parties%2C%20their%20character%20and%20social%20status.%20A%20very%20technical%20and%20hyper-sensitive%20approach%20would%20prove%20to%20be%20disastrous%20for%20the%20very%20institution%20of%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20main%20sufferers%20in%20matrimonial%20disputes%20are%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20spouses%20fight%20with%20such%20venom%20in%20their%20heart%20that%20they%20do%20not%20think%20even%20for%20a%20second%20that%20if%20the%20marriage%20would%20come%20to%20an%20end%2C%20what%20will%20be%20the%20effect%20on%20their%20children.%20Divorce%20plays%20a%20very%20dubious%20role%20so%20far%20as%20the%20upbringing%20of%20the%20children%20is%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20reason%20why%20we%20are%20saying%20so%20is%20that%20instead%20of%20handling%20the%20whole%20issue%20delicately%2C%20the%20initiation%20of%20criminal%20proceedings%20would%20bring%20about%20nothing%20but%20hatred%20for%20each%20other.%20There%20may%20be%20cases%20of%20genuine%20ill-treatment%20and%20harassment%20by%20the%20husband%20and%20his%20family%20members%20towards%20the%20wife.%20The%20degree%20of%20such%20ill-treatment%20or%20harassment%20may%20vary%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20the%20police%20machinery%20should%20be%20resorted%20to%20as%20a%20measure%20of%20last%20resort%20in%20matrimonial%20disputes%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20it%20cannot%20be%20utilised%20for%20holding%20the%20husband%20at%20ransom%20so%20that%20he%20could%20be%20squeezed%20by%20the%20wife%20at%20the%20instigation%20of%20her%20parents%20or%20relatives%20or%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20all%20cases%2C%20where%20the%20wife%20complains%20of%20harassment%20or%20ill-treatment%2C%20section%20498A%20of%20the%20IPC%20cannot%20be%20applied%20mechanically.%20No%20FIR%20is%20complete%20without%20sections%20506(2)%20and%20323%20of%20the%20IPC.%20Every%20matrimonial%20conduct%2C%20which%20may%20cause%20annoyance%20to%20the%20other%2C%20may%20not%20amount%20to%20cruelty.%20Mere%20trivial%20irritations%2C%20quarrels%20between%20spouses%2C%20which%20happen%20in%20day-to-day%20married%20life%2C%20may%20also%20not%20amount%20to%20cruelty%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20man%20and%20his%20family%20members%20allegedly%20demanded%20dowry%20and%20caused%20mental%20and%20physical%20trauma%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20said%20the%20woman's%20family%20had%20spent%20a%20large%20sum%20at%20the%20time%20of%20her%20wedding%20and%20also%20handed%20over%20her%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bstreedhan%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20husband%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20wedding%2C%20the%20husband%20and%20his%20family%20allegedly%20started%20harassing%20her%20on%20the%20false%20pretext%20that%20she%20had%20failed%20to%20discharge%20her%20duties%20as%20a%20wife%20and%20daughter-in-law%20and%20pressuring%20her%20for%20more%20dowry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20a%20plain%20reading%20of%20the%20FIR%20and%20the%20chargesheet%20indicates%20that%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20the%20woman%20are%20quite%20vague%2C%20general%20and%20sweeping%2C%20specifying%20no%20instances%20of%20criminal%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20also%20pertinent%20to%20note%20that%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20no%20specific%20date%20or%20time%20of%20the%20alleged%20offence%20or%20offences%20has%20been%20disclosed.%20Even%20the%20police%20thought%20fit%20to%20drop%20the%20proceedings%20against%20the%20other%20members%20of%20the%20appellant's%20(husband)%20family.%20Thus%2C%20we%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20the%20respondent%20no.%202%20(woman)%20was%20nothing%20but%20a%20counterblast%20to%20the%20divorce%20petition%20and%20also%2C%20the%20domestic%20violence%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20foregoing%20reasons%2C%20we%20have%20reached%20the%20conclusion%20that%20if%20the%20criminal%20proceedings%20are%20allowed%20to%20continue%20against%20the%20appellant%2C%20the%20same%20will%20be%20nothing%20short%20of%20an%20abuse%20of%20the%20process%20of%20law%20and%20travesty%20of%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714762140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftolerance-foundation-of-sound-marriage-supreme-court-in-dowry-case-5583407%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20said%20tolerance%20and%20respect%20are%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20sound%20marriage%20and%20petty%20quibbles%20should%20not%20be%20blown%20out%20of%20proportion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftolerance-foundation-of-sound-marriage-supreme-court-in-dowry-case-5583407%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftolerance-foundation-of-sound-marriage-supreme-court-in-dowry-case-5583407%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftolerance-foundation-of-sound-marriage-supreme-court-in-dowry-case-5583407%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWin%20Rae%20Bareli%20Before...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gary%20Kasparov%20On%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Love%20For%20Chess%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20favourite%20chess%20player%20Garry%20Kasparov%20appears%20to%20have%20taken%20note%20of%20his%20fondness%20for%20the%20game%20and%20has%20some%20advice%20for%20him%20--%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20win%20Rae%20Bareli%20before%20challenging%20for%20the%20top%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20legend%2C%20who%20retired%20from%20competitive%20chess%20in%202005%2C%20was%20r