ia.com%2F292438%2Fmango-man-of-india-haji-kalimullah-khan-won-padma-shri-for-growing-1300-varieties%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganically%20grown%20mangoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20their%20farm%20right%20to%20the%20comfort%20of%20your%20home.%20Looking%20back%20at%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20Prashant%20Powle%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20platform%20says%20that%20it%20was%20the%20best%20decision%20he%20made%20to%20quit%20the%20corporate%20sector%20and%20start%20this%20initiative.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20served%20around%2035%2C000%20customers%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir.%20Our%20mangoes%20are%20naturally%20grown%20and%20ripened%20through%20the%20Vedic%20harvesting%20(a%20traditional%20method%20where%20mangoes%20are%20harvested%20from%203.20%20AM%20until%20sunrise).%E2%80%9D%20As%20Powle%20explains%2C%20the%20mangoes%20are%20positively%20affected%20by%20the%20ozone%20levels%20during%20this%20time.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20use%20any%20chemicals%20for%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20emphasises.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20burn%20cow%20dung%2C%20and%20remove%20carbon%20dioxide%20and%20other%20gases%20from%20the%20emitted%20mix%20while%20keeping%20oxygen%20and%20ethylene.%20These%20help%20the%20mango%20ripen.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20A%20dozen%20costs%20anywhere%20from%20Rs%201%2C300%20to%20Rs%202%2C000%20depending%20on%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContact%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falphonsomango.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Falphonsomango.in%2F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Villa%20Mart%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201760px)%20100vw%2C%201760px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG20230226121638_11zon-1677675596_11zon-1713353707.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C